Package de.mpg.aai.shhaa.resolver

Interface Summary
AttributeResolverModule interface for modules of AttributeResolverHandler, defines methods to resolve (load/retrieve/fetch from where ever) attributes
 

Class Summary
AttributeResolverHandler main attribute composition/resolving handler, invokes its registered (AttributeResolverHandler.resolverModules resolver modules and processes them one after another
JaasAttbResolver implementation of AttributeResolverModule to plug-in JAAS for attribute-resolving; takes the jaas config file SECTION name from the configuration and invokes jaas: enables client developers to add thus their own implementations to resolve attributes for the given Subject (and add them as AuthAttribute to the Subject's public credentials
ShibHeaderAttbResolver implementation of AttributeResolverModule to lookup shibboleth attributes from the request http header (shibboleth service provider header attributes)
 

Exception Summary
ResolveException exception indicates issues in attribute composition/resolving
